                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h3
                            class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200"
                        >
                            Gemini
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                            My primary reasoning engine for complex context
                            windows and multimodal analysis.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
